OL,3,CImmigration reforms for 'complete
OL,4,Creset' to be introduced in Parliament
OL,6,FThe legislative measures are the first
OL,7,Fpolicy changes to be introduced from
OL,8,Fthe Government's Immigration White
OL,9,FPaper to tighten controls and cut
OL,10,Fmigration to the UK.
OL,12,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said:"We
OL,13,Fare delivering a complete reset of our
OL,14,Fimmigration system to restore proper
OL,15,Fcontrol and order, after the previous
OL,16,Fgovernment allowed net migration to
OL,17,Fquadruple in four years.
