OL,3,CImmigration reforms for 'complete
OL,4,Creset' to be introduced in Parliament
OL,6,FFurther measures from the White Paper
OL,7,Fsuch as increasing English language
OL,8,Frequirements and raising the
OL,9,Fimmigration skills charge are also
OL,10,Fexpected to be in place by the end of
OL,11,Fthe year.
OL,13,FThe White Paper is aimed at reducing
OL,14,Fnumbers, clamping down on abuses of
OL,15,Fthe system and ending a reliance on
OL,16,Fcheap foreign labour.
