OL,3,CImmigration reforms for 'complete
OL,4,Creset' to be introduced in Parliament
OL,6,FHome Office estimates indicate that
OL,7,Fchanges from the plan could reduce the
OL,8,Fnumber of people coming to the UK by
OL,9,Fup to 100,000 per year, when looking
OL,10,Fat eight of its proposals including on
OL,11,Fstudy and work routes and a higher
OL,12,Flevel of English language requirement.
OL,14,FBut the move to scrap care worker
OL,15,Fvisas has sparked concerns from the
OL,16,Fsector, with GMB national officer Will
OL,17,FDalton describing the decision as
OL,18,F"potentially catastrophic" as the care
OL,19,Fsector was "utterly reliant on migrant
OL,20,Fworkers" and still had more than
OL,21,F130,000 vacancies across the country.
